data.description: Home, sweet home! Experience the comfort and warmth of this charming residence in the peaceful Casa Grande Townhomes. Providing 3 beds, 2.5 baths, and a 2-car garage. Discover a semi-open layout paired with a large living room with exposed beams! Designer paint and tile flooring with wood laminate in all the right places enhance the inviting vibe. The kitchen boasts SS appliances, granite counters, wood cabinetry, and a peninsula w/breakfast bar. Head upstairs to find the cozy bedrooms! The primary bedroom has two closets and an ensuite with dual sinks. You'll LOVE the private patio, a perfect spot for relaxing or enjoying BBQ! Take advantage of convenient access to the nearby community pool, just a stone's throw from your unit. Excellent Casa Grande location! Don't miss this opportunity!
